---
title: Coconut Curry Shrimp with Chickpeas served with Basmati Rice & topped with Yogurt
description: Curries are one of those meals that warms your heart and your belly, and tonight’s vegetarian version is no exception. Chickpeas, onion, and bell pepper get a super savory treatment in a coconut-based curry sauce. Toss that over rice, add a dollop of yogurt and a sprinkle of cilantro, and you have yourself one soul-satisfying meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63fe35d8db3e0401490898c0-5a9ba1b5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64dd0857ef3d37ebd500fff4.pdf
nutrition:
